org.apache.uima.mediawiki.ae.factory
Class MWAnnotator

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.uima.mediawiki.ae.factory.MWAnnotator

public class MWAnnotator
extends java.lang.Object

This class handles the creation of all the annotations for the CAS. The document builder calls the method provided by this factory to populate the CAS with annotations while processing the content.

For now, we handle Header, Section, Paragraph and Link annotations.

Author:
Maxime Bury <Maxime.bury@gmail.com>

end

public static void end(java.lang.String type,
                       int offset)
This method handles the closing of various annotations. For now, it handles closing headers, sections, tables and it also closes the unclosed section when we reach the end of the document.

Parameters:
type - the type of the annotation we are closing.
offset - the ending offset.
